P(R) represents a pattern drawn by Julia in R rows. The following pattern represents P(5):

* 
* * 
* * * 
* * * * 
* * * * *
Write a query to print the pattern P(20).

-----------------------------------------------------------------Solution---------------------------------------------------



CREATE PROCEDURE print (IN n INTEGER) BEGIN DECLARE x INTEGER; SET x = n;

WHILE n > 0 DO
    SELECT REPEAT('* ', x - n + 1);
    SET n = n - 1 ;
END WHILE;

CALL print(20);
